engine.component

Class ParticleTrailComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • engine.component.Component
      • engine.component.ParticleTrailComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UpdateableComponent

    public class ParticleTrailComponent
extends Component
implements UpdateableComponent
    Specifies a component that will allow an entity to have a particle trail behind it based off certain parameters.

    Marco

                              org.jsfml.graphics.Color mainColor,
                              int numparticles,
                              float lifetime)
        Parameters:
        entity - The active entity
        minSpeed - The minimum speed an entity must have before the particle trail can take effect
        speeddamp - The damping factor applied to the speed of the particles
        freq - The rate at which particles are spawned
        mainColor - The main colour of the particles
        numparticles - The number of particles spawned at a time
        lifetime - The average lifetime of a particle
